As a senior Elementary School Teacher Except Special Education, I will ensure that I enforce the administration policies and rules governing students by following the school's code of conduct and student handbook. This includes maintaining a positive and respectful classroom environment, promoting student safety and well-being, and addressing any behavioral or disciplinary issues promptly and fairly. I will also communicate regularly with parents and guardians to keep them informed of their child's progress and any issues that may arise. Additionally, I will work closely with school administrators and other teachers to ensure that our policies and procedures are consistent and effective.
